  "pageTitle": "C&D 废弃物利用线",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">C&amp;D 废物箱 详情</p>\n        <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">C&D 废弃物利用线</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">关于一体化C&D 废弃物回收线路的参考，生产回收骨料和分离可回收材料。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"construction-waste-utilization\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-waste-utilization-timeline-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">参考时间线</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-waste-utilization-timeline-title\">从填埋压力到可回收的输出水流</h2>\n          <p>案例按买方评估流程排序：背景、合作单位、限制、解以及对比前后对比。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例 详情 时间线\">\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">项目背景</p>\n              <h3>建筑和装饰废弃物的利用价值</h3>\n              <p>该项目将混合的建筑和装饰废弃物处理成可重复使用的输出流，而不是直接将材料引导至填埋压力。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>物料类别</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 流</strong><span>建筑与装饰浪费</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>输出方向</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">3 输出</strong><span>骨料 / 金属 / 轻质材料</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作单位</p>\n              <h3>匿名区域建筑废物利用公司</h3>\n              <p>合作单位正在扩大骨料回收，需要一条可参考的线路，供买家根据废物类型、场地状况和设备范围进行比较。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>操作员类型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 地区团队</strong><span>废物利用公司</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>评审重点</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 检查</strong><span>材料 / 场地 / 范围 / 视频</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">实际限制</p>\n              <h3>户外车场的后勤安排塑造了线路布局</h3>\n              <p>布局必须考虑装载机供料、设备基础区域、骨料堆场、金属收集和轻质物料分离处理。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>场地面积</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 区域</strong><span>给料至储藏</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>初选限制</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 场地</strong><span>户外物流足迹</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解决方案</p>\n              <h3>70 t/h Lion One集成分离线</h3>\n              <p>设备范围结合了送料、破碎、筛分、磁性分离、气流分离、输送、粉尘控制接口和输出收集。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>容量参考</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">70 t/h</strong><span>Lion One 线</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>核心流程</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 工序</strong><span>压碎 / 显示屏 / 磁铁 / 气流</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前后对比</p>\n              <h3>参考包显示了更清晰的回收路径</h3>\n              <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\">\n                <div><span>之前</span><strong>混合场地材料，路由清晰度低</strong><p>建筑和装饰废弃物需要多次处理步骤，才能看到可回收的部分。</p></div>\n                <div><span>之后</span><strong>从给料到库存的综合流程</strong><p>视频占地面积涵盖送料、破碎、筛分、磁性分离、气流分离以及最终输出堆。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>视频范围</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">6 步骤</strong><span>供给输出</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section industrial-rfq-section ai-layout-reference\" aria-label=\"案例操作\">\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求参考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
